    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You've gotta see this absolute beauty! It\u2019s been seriously babied and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014honestly, it's in flawless shape. No scratches, no dents, and the interior still has that fresh feel. It drives like an absolute dream! I've taken such good care of it, and I'm looking for someone who will love it just as much as I have. If you want a ride that looks and feels brand new, this is the one! \u2728",
