    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute gem for the discerning enthusiast. This vehicle is in truly impeccable, showroom-ready condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior boasts its original factory finish with a deep, mirror-like luster, free from any swirls, chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in a pristine state; the premium leather upholstery still retains its factory-fresh scent and shows zero signs of wear or creasing. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver assistance features, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is flawless, supported by a comprehensive folder of service records performed exclusively at authorized dealerships. It has never seen a winter road and has been spared from the elements. This is not just a used car; it is a perfectly preserved example of engineering excellence. For the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is the one.",
      "price": 48500.0,
