    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You seriously have to see this absolute gem in person\u2014it\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s in truly pristine condition inside and out. It drives like a total dream and looks even better. I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to fall in love with it instantly. Let's get you behind the wheel for a look!",
